c025cc12-4c92-4585-8083-e54b75556e39.name: VM Count - Non-Windows  Powered ON
c025cc12-4c92-4585-8083-e54b75556e39.formula: count(${adaptertype=VMWARE, objecttype=VirtualMachine, metric=config|guestFullName, depth=8, where=(!($value contains 'Microsoft') && ${metric=sys|poweredOn} == 1)})
c025cc12-4c92-4585-8083-e54b75556e39.description: Count of Non-windows VMs which are Powered ON

2971ad72-9629-4771-a776-dce39032a519.name: VM Count - Windows Powered ON
2971ad72-9629-4771-a776-dce39032a519.formula: count(${adaptertype=VMWARE, objecttype=VirtualMachine, metric=config|guestFullName, depth=8, where=($value contains 'Windows' && ${metric=sys|poweredOn} == 1)})
2971ad72-9629-4771-a776-dce39032a519.description: Count of Windows VMs Powered ON
